00043 void test_bar(string file)
00044 {
00045   TagValuePairType param;
00046         CBARFileData bar;
00047         bar.SetFileName(file.c_str());
00048         if (bar.Exists())
00049         {
00050                 bar.Read();
00051 
00052                 cout << "Version = " << bar.GetVersion() << endl;
00053                 cout << "#Seqs = " << bar.GetNumberSequences() << endl;
00054                 cout << "#Cols = " << bar.GetNumberColumns() << endl;
00055                 cout << "#Params = " << bar.GetNumberParameters() << endl;
00056 
00057                 for (int iparam=0; iparam<bar.GetNumberParameters(); iparam++)
00058                 {
00059                         param = bar.GetParameter(iparam);
00060                         cout << param.Tag << " = " << param.Value << endl;
00061                 }
00062 
00063                 for (int iseq=0; iseq<bar.GetNumberSequences(); iseq++)
00064                 {
00065                         CGDACSequenceResultItem res;
00066                         bar.GetResults(iseq, res);
00067 
00068                         cout << "Name = " << res.GetName() << endl;
00069                         cout << "Group = " << res.GetGroupName() << endl;
00070                         cout << "Version = " << res.GetVersion() << endl;
00071                         cout << "#Pts = " << res.GetNumberDataPoints() << endl;
00072                         cout << "#Cols = " << res.GetNumberColumns() << endl;
00073 
00074                         for (int iseqparam=0; iseqparam<res.GetNumberParameters(); iseqparam++)
00075                         {
00076         TagValuePairType &param = res.GetParameter(iseqparam);
00077                                 cout << param.Tag << "=" << param.Value << endl;
00078                         }
00079 
00080                         BarSequenceResultData data;
00081                         for (int ipt=0; ipt<res.GetNumberDataPoints(); ipt++)
00082                         {
00083                                 for (int icol=0; icol<res.GetNumberColumns(); icol++)
00084                                 {
00085                                         res.GetData(ipt, icol, data);
00086 
00087                                         switch (res.GetColumnType(icol))
00088                                         {
00089                                         case BAR_DATA_INTEGER:
00090                                                 cout << data.iValue << endl;
00091                                                 break;
00092 
00093                                         case BAR_DATA_FLOAT:
00094                                                 cout << data.fValue << endl;
00095                                                 break;
00096 
00097             // Die if it isnt handled.
00098           default:
00099             assert(0);
00100                                         }
00101                                 }
00102                         }
00103                 }
00104         }
